### Update tailwind to v4

GEL v1 now uses tailwind 4 for its styling. Follow the update instruction at [Tailwind CSS Upgrade Guide](https://tailwindcss.com/docs/upgrade-guide).

### Update ui package

Follow the installation instructions on how to use the latest version of the ui package [here](/get-started/developers/installation)

For detailed component changes refer to the [changelog](https://github.com/WestpacGEL/GEL-next/blob/release/1.0.0/packages/ui/CHANGELOG.md)
